Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.map

Class Pawn

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.map.Pawn
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cell
Direct Known Subclasses:
Worker
public abstract class Pawn
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cell
Abstract class that represents a generic pawn, giving indication for how any object (different from a block) can behave on the board. In our game it can only be a worker but some advanced God power may require the use of tokens, therefore making it easier to add them into the game
